                     <interp inst="t18490820-1626-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="simpleLarceny"></interp>, stealing 1 coat, value 3<hi rend="italic">l</hi>.; the goods of <persName id="t18490820-name-740" type="victimName">
